text: == Events == * War between Rome and Parthia starts because of the invasion of Armenia by Vologases I. He replaced the Roman supported ruler with his brother Tiridates of Parthia. * Publius Clodius Thrasea Paetus becomes a consul in Rome. * The Jianwu era of the Eastern Han Dynasty changes to the Jianwuzhongyuan era. == Births == * Gaius Cornelius Tacitus, Roman historian (d. 117 AD) Category:50s
